                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-end gap-6 text-sm py-2 px-1">
                    <div class="flex gap-2 items-center"><span class="w-3 h-3 bg-skin-accent opacity-20 rounded"></span> <span class="opacity-70">TV = 継続価値 (Terminal Value)</span></div>
                    <div class="flex gap-2 items-center font-bold"><span>合計現在価値 (EV):</span> <span class="text-skin-accent">{reportData.dcf_valuation.enterprise_value ? '$' + (reportData.dcf_valuation.enterprise_value / 1e9).toFixed(2) + 'B' : '---'}</span></div>
