                  </h3>
                  <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-skin-line">
                    <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-skin-line text-sm">
                      <tbody class="divide-y divide-skin-line">
                        <tr class="bg-skin-fill/5"><td class="px-4 py-2 opacity-70">DCF予測成長率 (1-5Y) <span class="text-[10px] font-normal opacity-50 block leading-tight">※モデルが推定する将来成長率</span></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-right font-medium text-skin-accent">{(reportData.dcf_valuation.growth_1_5y * 100).toFixed(2)}%</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 opacity-70">必要成長率 (現在株価ベース) <span class="text-[10px] font-normal opacity-50 block leading-tight">※現在株価 (${reportData.dcf_valuation.current_price.toFixed(2)}) を正当化するために必要な年平均成長率</span></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-right font-medium">{(reportData.dcf_valuation.reverse_growth * 100).toFixed(2)}%</td></tr>
                        <tr class={`font-bold border-t-2 border-skin-line ${
                          reportData.dcf_valuation.reverse_growth <= reportData.dcf_valuation.growth_1_5y
