                        }`}>
                          <td class="px-4 py-2">実現可能性判定 <span class="text-[10px] font-normal opacity-50 block leading-tight">※必要成長率 ≤ DCF予測 なら割安、超過なら割高傾向</span></td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-2 text-right">
                            {reportData.dcf_valuation.reverse_growth <= reportData.dcf_valuation.growth_1_5y
