              {/* Technical Methodology Section */}
              <div class="mt-8">
                <details class="group bg-skin-fill/10 border border-skin-line rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                  <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-skin-fill/20 transition-colors">
                    <span class="font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-skin-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                      </svg>
                      DCF算出ロジックの数学的定義 (Technical Methodology)
                    </span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                    </svg>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="p-6 border-t border-skin-line space-y-8 bg-skin-card/50">

                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-skin-accent mb-4 border-l-4 border-skin-accent pl-2">1. 割引率 (Discount Rate: WACC)</h4>
                      <p class="text-sm mb-4">資本資産価格モデル (CAPM) に基づき、株主資本コストと有利子負債コストを加重平均します。</p>

                      <div class="bg-skin-fill/20 p-6 rounded-md space-y-6 overflow-x-auto text-center font-serif">
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
                          <p class="text-skin-accent font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">■ 株主資本コスト (Cost of Equity - CAPM)</p>
